# Hero Images

This directory contains background images for the homepage hero section.

## Current Images:
- hero-bg.jpg - Main homepage hero background

## Guidelines:
- Recommended size: 1920x1080px (16:9 aspect ratio)
- Mobile size: 768x1024px (3:4 aspect ratio) for mobile-first design
- File size: Keep under 500KB after compression
- Format: JPEG or WebP preferred